{
  "texts": [
    "• Do not annotate substances or medicinal herbs comprising the traditional formula.",
    "• Annotate the most specific disease mentions with maximum span.",
    "(e.g., \"Insulin-dependent diabetes mellitus\" rather than \"diabetes mellitus\".)",
    "• Annotate all synonymous mentions, including abbreviations possible to assume though not specified in the abstract.",
    "• Annotate each disease and symptom mentions separately, when the disease or symptom induced by disease."
  ]
}